  "notes": [
    "On-board addressable RGB LED on GPIO27 (WS2812 protocol \u2014 not a plain GPIO LED).",
    "UART0 (GPIO11/12) carries the WireLab protocol on this board; the pins are reserved.",
    "GPIO15 position is NC unless the module has no in-package PSRAM.",
    "ADC1 channels 0-5 sit on GPIO1-6."
